{"tid":1265163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 距離71仲有兩日 但係宣傳極度唔夠","createTime":"2019-06-29T05:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T14:32:23.000Z","uid":40431,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dbdfcc8312bc34d3e4420a497083bdf0d63e9e3d","tid":1265163,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:12:44.000Z","msg":"69 612 616都要至少兩三日宣傳先聚到人，但係而家基本上完全冇之前嗰種鋪天蓋地嘅呼召去叫人上街。<br />\n其實近幾次都係，因為行動安排得太密唔夠時間將消息傳開，所以人數都唔夠多。<br />\n而家件事拖得太耐，加上普通市民軍心開始散，71好唔樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n入到嚟見到嘅話麻煩每人喺FB/IG出一個post叫班去過69/616嘅朋友71再上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港共唔肯回應四大訴求又唔理民意割咗中環海濱俾解放軍，兩單加埋冇理由會少人過之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716922f478f23c26a202964662183c8388211db0","tid":1265163,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0d20719ccb8367d517dde6e9423ff673f96f27","tid":1265163,"uid":54228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGOguFB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGOguFB.png&h=6b59ace6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73bc33c0b8d59117d2404943d301ed755ad74cc0","tid":1265163,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:13:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">七一野餐會 <br />\n人數決定一切<br />\n</span></span><br />\n&mdash; 唔 理 衝 唔 衝 ， 迫 爆 金 紫 荊 &mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1265048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1265048</a><br />\n<br />\n【七一升級&middot;屌爆升旗禮】不舉係近來對政府施壓最重大嘅機會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1264575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1264575</a><br />\n<br />\n71 香港不舉行動 計劃大綱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/12637